Text:
@zarquonp The crack *is* separate. After unzipping, you'll see the install DMG and the crack installer.

This is the Mac OS X version of Amplitube 3.9.1, and can be used as an AU or VST plugin in any Mac DAW.

I use Logic, and Amplitube shows up automatically as an AU when you restart Logic (or rescan for plugins) after install.
